item.description: × MINSITTHAR HD Wallpaper ❮ ❯ In the mysterious village of the East there was once a hero, "Holy Spear" Minsitthar, who had saved his kingdom from danger. He was once the Prince of Mahar Pura and served in the Forces from his youth. After adulthood he was respectfully called one of the "Four Great Generals" of Mahar Pura with his remarkable achievements. Minsitthar was invincible in wars, which earned the trust of the King and his people.
